<HEADLINE> Founder Group Becomes Major Electronic Publishing Supplier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 16 (Xinhua) -- At least 300 Chinese
newspapers are using electronic publishing technology from Beijing
University's Founder Group Corp, China's leading supplier.
</P>
<P>
According to the corporation, 20 more papers will start using
its color editing and publishing system next year, giving them at
least 20 pages a day.
</P>
<P>
In addition, more than 80 newspapers are hooked to the
company's comprehensive press network, which provides the
newest information worldwide.
</P>
